{"data":[{"id":562600846,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8dfa05cbe4a4e8aa0253fc367b79626b","url_token":"xie-dong-liu-25","name":"叶东流","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4a4fdd24d966ec532764c7696fa47cef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4a4fdd24d966ec532764c7696fa47cef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8dfa05cbe4a4e8aa0253fc367b79626b","user_type":"people","headline":"自由而无用的灵魂","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":192,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562600846","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546107156,"updated_time":1546279019,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":4,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e修改回答：题主可能真的是神经有点问题，我对鼓励态度持保留意见。（手动滑稽）\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e先摆观点：就现在来看，这位同学确实有些不知天高地厚了。不过我们如果嘲讽打击，确实也不应当。把事情讲明白，道理讲清楚，就好，他接不接受那又是另一回事了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个其实 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\" data-hash=\"77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\"\u003e@Vayne嫒\u003c/a\u003e 这位答主的回答说得很好，高中只是大学的敲门砖，大学才是学术之门的敲门砖，进了学术之门才可能看见哥猜的大门，至于能不能敲开就是你的本事了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e到现在，看了很久的戏，也吃了许多瓜，还是忍不住要写点东西。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先声明，我不是学数学的，也不是学理工医科的，不过我们可以类比。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一句证明哥猜相当于什么？各位可以看下面三句话：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e①我释读出了十个甲骨文，过几天给你们看，有理有据。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e②我能给自由意志与恶的问题做一个逻辑完整自洽的公理化分析，过几天你们看。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e③我挖出了虞墟，证明了二里头之前的中国北方有国家形态的文明，过几天给你们看考古报告。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e①，自从清末民国以来，中国无数文字学家、训诂学家、考据学家、考古学家都想多释读一个甲骨文，现在已经到了瓶颈。别说释读出来了，提出一个有道理的猜想就可以学界瞩目了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e②，吵了一千五百年以上的问题，无数哲学家、神学家试图给出一个解答，但到现在为止，没有一个逻辑是没有漏洞的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e③，中国人心心念念几千年的事情，现代考古学研究了几十年的事情，夏商周断代工程都做白了一群人的头发，你说挖出虞墟是不是可以让世界震动？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e尽管如此，我还是知道上面三句话的分量其实不会重于证出哥猜，哥猜是数学的皇冠明珠，在许多人看来更有一种神圣性。可能只有自由意志的问题对本学界的学者具有同样的神圣性了。要证出哥猜，需要的智慧也许还要超过你编出一个能蒙骗万千世人的虞墟。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们说文人相轻，特别他还是一个名不见经传的高中生，那么他被一群人嘲讽也是正常，不加以打击的话如何显示其所学的专业性？实话说，要是哪个高中生说“我能给古代汉语重新断代，而且证据充足，可以取代现行的几个体系”估计我也会上去骂一顿，人家王力高本汉郑张尚芳那么多大师都扯不清楚的你算个什么？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e确实，劝诫和说理就足够了，讽刺还是有些过了。不过我们也要想到一个问题，有些人学了专业数学，甚至就是学数学专业的，当他们看到这么一个可以说是不知天高地厚的回答时，他一定会产生“这个人在侮辱数学界的皇冠明珠”的想法，也难怪他们要讽刺。至于那些毫无知识背景就讽刺的，大家就当是抬杠了，看着好玩随手评几句，其它别管了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后还是希望题主能先想办法进入学术的领域再思考证明哥猜的问题。如果题主都进不了这个领域，那么你证出的可能性大概就是零，那种几何概型里点到一个点的概率，而被众人舆论消费的可能性是一。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"修改回答：题主可能真的是神经有点问题，我对鼓励态度持保留意见。（手动滑稽）先摆观点：就现在来看，这位同学确实有些不知天高地厚了。不过我们如果嘲讽打击，确实也不应当。把事情讲明白，道理讲清楚，就好，他接不接受那又是另一回事了。这个其实 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\" data-hash=\"77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\"\u003e@Vayn…\u003c/a\u003e","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=471\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=469\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2547}}
